# Vendored CivMC plugin primitives. Reviewers MUST verify these hashes when
# accepting any PR that touches libs/. CI runs `shasum -a 256 -c` against this
# file on every build.
#
# Provenance: built from the CivMC monorepo at
# https://github.com/CivMC/Civ (grepsedawk fork: https://github.com/grepsedawk/Civ)
# pinned to commit a5e1ce3e543fca771b5afb2d4ca4dbcfdb5cdae6. The published
# GitHub Releases on the per-plugin repos (CivMC/CivModCore, CivMC/NameLayer,
# CivMC/JukeAlert) are stale relative to the monorepo HEAD, so we build from
# the monorepo `plugins/<name>` modules instead.
#
# To refresh: rebuild the matching `plugins/<name>-paper` module from the
# monorepo, replace the jar, recompute with `shasum -a 256 libs/<file>.jar`,
# update the matching line, and bump the pinned commit above.
#
# acf-paper is the Aikar ACF command framework — an api() dep of
# civmodcore-paper that is NOT shaded into civmodcore's jar, so we vendor it
# directly from co.aikar:acf-paper:0.5.1-SNAPSHOT.

# civmodcore-paper.jar — CivModCore 3.0.6 — plugins/civmodcore-paper @ CivMC/Civ a5e1ce3
b953bd2be15fddc8fdac81d7fb904e8d521183fbdf91ec8dfd12b533d183251a  civmodcore-paper.jar

# namelayer-paper.jar — NameLayer 3.0.6 — plugins/namelayer-paper @ CivMC/Civ a5e1ce3
219beed14c48c515186ce4537ff28fa9edf029a50e4f8627f55ef623efae2d2b  namelayer-paper.jar

# jukealert-paper.jar — JukeAlert 3.0.8 — plugins/jukealert-paper @ CivMC/Civ a5e1ce3
8b974845eb2dc83fe0372d16d3c1290d71f5eb951d54deda38de143685b77ed0  jukealert-paper.jar

# acf-paper.jar — co.aikar:acf-paper:0.5.1-SNAPSHOT — https://repo.aikar.co/content/groups/aikar/ (src: https://github.com/aikar/commands)
ff52258bad52ee326f8d2d9a4bdb3c821d5a99b1e8d2b0b70ff68454d899fdec  acf-paper.jar

